                <project id="12310865" key="CASSANDRA">Apache Cassandra</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Steps to reproduce:&lt;br/&gt;
&lt;a href=&quot;https://gist.github.com/sargun/6771123&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://gist.github.com/sargun/6771123&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

