                            <comment id="13782440" author="iamaleksey" created="Mon, 30 Sep 2013 23:49:47 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;1.2 is unaffected, this is a 2.0 regression. The issue is not batch-related, something&apos;s likely wrong with resolve().&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
